---
import Container from "@/components/ui/Container.astro";
import SectionHeader from "@/components/ui/SectionHeader.astro";
import BaseLayout from "@/layouts/BaseLayout.astro";
---

<BaseLayout
  title="Writer"
  description="UMC PRODUCT 블로그와 릴리즈 노트 MDX 초안을 생성하는 작성 도구입니다."
>
  <Container class="py-14 max-[760px]:py-10">
    <SectionHeader
      eyebrow="Writer"
      title="작성 도구"
      description="작성할 콘텐츠 타입을 선택하세요. 두 도구 모두 Markdown 미리보기, MDX 생성, TECH_BLOG 이미지 업로드를 지원합니다."
    />

    <div class="grid grid-cols-2 gap-4 max-[760px]:grid-cols-1">
      <a
        class="grid gap-3 rounded-lg border border-ds-divider bg-ds-surface p-5 transition-colors hover:border-ds-primary-soft hover:bg-ds-hover"
        href="/write/blog"
      >
        <span class="text-label-3 uppercase text-ds-primary">Blog</span>
        <strong class="text-heading-5 text-ds-text-strong">Tech Blog Writer</strong>
        <span class="text-body-2 text-ds-text-muted">
          title, description, parts, authors 기반의 블로그 MDX 초안을 생성합니다.
        </span>
      </a>

      <a
        class="grid gap-3 rounded-lg border border-ds-divider bg-ds-surface p-5 transition-colors hover:border-ds-primary-soft hover:bg-ds-hover"
        href="/write/release"
      >
        <span class="text-label-3 uppercase text-ds-primary">Release</span>
        <strong class="text-heading-5 text-ds-text-strong">Release Note Writer</strong>
        <span class="text-body-2 text-ds-text-muted">
          version, platform, releasedAt 기반의 릴리즈 노트 MDX 초안을 생성합니다.
        </span>
      </a>
    </div>
  </Container>
</BaseLayout>
